<title>Ice Golem</title>
<!--#include virtual="/content_header.html" -->
<h2>Ice Golem</h2></br>
Fought during <a href="/chapters/chapter_two.html#blizzard_p">Chapter Two</a> in the <a href="/settings/blizzard.html">Blizzard</a>.</br>
Golem made of ice.</br>
Summoned by the <a href="/monsters/summoner.html">Summoner</a>.</br>
The Golem's spawn takes about 2-5 seconds to gather the ice mass together and form.</br>
If the Protagonist attacks the mass during the spawn, the Golem shatters.</br></br>

